data.description: Welcome to This True Masterpiece and Absolute Titan of a Home in the Highly Sought Community of Mira Mosa! *RATE BUY-DOWN OPPORTUNITY* The Largest Floor Plan That This Pristine Community Has to Offer, This, Almost 3,700 Sqft Home Boasts NO HOA or MELLO ROOS! This Immaculate Home Includes PAID SOLAR, Water Filtration & Reverse Osmosis, Heated Pool & Hot Tub, Top-of-the-Line Smart Systems, Dual Split AC Systems, and Much Much More! All 5 Bedrooms are Very Generously Sized, Including 2 Extra Loft Spaces, SEPARATE From the original size. Approaching the Home, Capture the Serene Mountainous View the the East. Step into the Capturing Great room with a Guest Suite, Half Bath, and Potential Office Space to the Left. Open Dining Room Directly Ahead and the Entrance to the Living Room & Kitchen Peeking Through the Right. The Smart Appliances, Advanced ADT Security System, and Lighting through the Home Provide a Light and Bright Atmosphere for all Types of Entertaining for Friends & Family! Making your way up the stairs, the Vast Master Bedroom Flows into Captivating Views and Leads into the Resort-Style Bathroom with it's own TV, Soaking Tub, and even Heating/Drying Towel Rack. Across from the Master is the Potential Theater Room that Trickles into the Remainder of the Hall Way into THREE Other Bedrooms and the Last Full Bath in the Home. Stepping into the Patio, Enjoy the Inevitable Tranquility with no Neighbors Directly Ahead, the Sunset, and a Glass of Wine as Your Day Winds Down. TheThird Car Garage, Multi-Headed Shower System, etc. are just Extras! Don't Miss Out!!
